--[[
	PROFESSIONAL ROBLOX GUI FRAMEWORK - ONE SCRIPT

	Paste this entire file into one LocalScript under:
	StarterPlayer > StarterPlayerScripts

	No ModuleScripts, folders, require calls, or loader scripts are needed.
	Add new features to INLINE_MODULES near the bottom of this file.

	Notes:
	- This script must run on the client because Roblox UI is player-specific.
	- DataStoreService is server-only. Config persistence therefore uses an
	  injected adapter. The built-in adapter preserves config for this session.
	  Supply ConfigAdapter with Load/Save methods for cross-session data.
]]

